<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>169</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung khua a tha pennak thlarau khua nih a kan awrh ko, A kum fatin
 mithiang mi kha an i khawm, Vancung khua pennak ni khua nih a kan naih
 chin ciahmah ko, Vancung pennak rung tlun cu a nai ko cang.

[C1]
   Vancung pennak thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Vancung pennak
   thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Ka thlarau i tim cang tuah, pumhnak muko
   an tum lai A lianngan, nun uk Pathian a lang lai.

[V2]
 Vancung khua Pathian thlarau khuatha ruahchannak lungthin in Mikhamhtu
 Pathian a langh lai kha kan hngak, A kan tlanh cang vawlei cung khuahrum
 rulhreu sal cannak in, Vancung pennak rung tlun cu a nai ko cang.

[C2]
   Vancung pennak thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Vancung pennak
   thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Ka thlarau i tim cang tuah, pumhnak muko
   an tum lai A lianngan, nun uk Pathian a lang lai.

[V3]
 Vancung pennak a tlun tikah a lian Pathian kan hmuh lai, Kan lu a
 kantu kha a lang hmasa lai, Hal-le-lui-jah a thi in a kan cawk
 thluachuahnak a si, Maw Pathian vancung pennak nih a kan naih.

[C3]
   Vancung pennak thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Vancung pennak
   thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Ka thlarau i tim cang tuah, pumhnak muko
   an tum lai A lianngan, nun uk Pathian a lang lai.

[V4]
 Khua sau ngannak ca hi vaw lei khua hna kha an re a thei, A rauh ca'h
 mi vialte an lung a rawk cang, Vancung kong kha bia ngai tein an
 thanuamter ko u si, Zeitintiah vancung pennak nai dengmang cang.

[C4]
   Vancung pennak thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Vancung pennak
   thlarau khua kha kan naih deng, Ka thlarau i tim cang tuah, pumhnak muko
   an tum lai A lianngan, nun uk Pathian a lang lai.</lyrics>
<title>PATHIAN PENNAK A NAI CANG CH169</title>
</song>